  ('dietitian-moex-11636', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Type 1糖尿病患生病時，下列處理何者較適宜？ 若食物攝取減少，應降低胰島素的劑量以預防低血糖 可採用少量多餐、高醣類之流質以預防低血糖 若未進食，則不必注射胰島素 使用靜脈營養，但不給葡萄糖', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11637', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '肝性腦病變的治療常會給病人乳酮糖 (lactulose)，下列何者並不是給予乳酮糖的主要目的？ 給予肝臟病人能量的補充  引起病人腹瀉  降低血液中的氨濃度  降低腸道的pH值', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11638', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於腎功能不良的病患而言，早期控制那兩種營養素的攝取，有助於延緩腎衰竭的速度？ 蛋白質與鉀  蛋白質與磷  磷與鉀  磷與鈣', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11639', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列食物中的成分，何者之腎臟溶質負荷 (renal solute load) 最大？ protein, Na  carbohydrate, fat  protein, carbohydrate  protein, fluid', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11640', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '收集一腎臟病患之24小時尿液為1200毫升，測得UUN為600毫克/100毫升，其當日飲食中蛋白質的攝取量為60 公克，則其氮平衡的數值為： +2.4  -1.6  +0.8  -0.6', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11641', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於糖尿病患血糖自我監控 (SMBG) 的敘述，下列何者正確？ 對Type 1 DM病人，建議每天在三餐飯前及睡前各執行一次 對Type 1 DM病人，建議每天在三餐飯後及睡前各執行一次 對Type 2 DM病人，建議每天在睡前及三餐飯後各執行一次，但一週只要3、4天即可 對使用胰島素的病人，最好在運動前後各執行一次', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
